{"tid":924995,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"平絕四小龍！碧海藍天三房狂劈270萬沽出","createTime":"2018-12-02T13:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T23:27:42.000Z","uid":174649,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cadd11271fea10a14cb4a6b8312e8034c81831d9","tid":924995,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T13:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181202/photo/bkn-20181202184801032-1202_00842_001_01p.jpg?20181202192147\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181202%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181202184801032-1202_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20181202192147&h=109795bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港置業文啟光表示，長沙灣碧海藍天3座低層8室，實用面積577方呎，三房間隔，9月開價1,150萬港元放售，上月已大手下調至950萬元，最後進一步減至880萬元售出，累減多達270萬元或約23.5%，呎價15,251元。<br />\n<br />\n上述更為同區四小龍今年首宗跌穿900萬元的三戶成交個案(另外3個屋苑為泓景臺、昇悅居及宇晴軒)，而該批屋苑上月全月錄10宗成交，較10月顯增1.5倍。"},{"pid":"c3e69c095fe4af4f64a7a711aa9a86cafd842dcc","tid":924995,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T14:21:02.000Z","msg":"低層唔計"},{"pid":"2f69bcc05739d3e17b614cf3d00dc2ab58f26cba","tid":924995,"uid":78791,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ed42762121bc67f3ec8066428847c32f96345d7","tid":924995,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T14:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc80b7f6abbff7336a0aae548024e18f09d101d2","tid":924995,"uid":7369,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T15:30:04.000Z","msg":"880萬我買兩間保升unun腳收租唔好！"},{"pid":"3e28026bc93e96579defc28e6fd56b082fc288f2","tid":924995,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc80b7f6abbff7336a0aae548024e18f09d101d2","tid":924995,"uid":7369,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T15:30:04.000Z","msg":"880萬我買兩間保升unun腳收租唔好！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"